House Bill 4088
Ordered by the House February 11
Including House Amendments dated February 11
Sponsored by Representative FRAGALA, Senators REYNOLDS, PROZANSKI, Representatives CHAICHI,
CHOTZEN, DOBSON, RIEKE SMITH, VALDERRAMA, Senators GELSER BLOUIN, MANNING JR,
